Calculate indirect emissions from purchased inputs

Source: R/calc_emissions_inputs.R
calc_emissions_inputs.Rd

Estimates CO2eq emissions from purchased inputs such as feeds, concentrates, fertilizers, and plastics with regional factors and uncertainty analysis.

Usage

calc_emissions_inputs(
  conc_kg = 0,
  fert_n_kg = 0,
  plastic_kg = 0,
  feed_grain_dry_kg = 0,
  feed_grain_wet_kg = 0,
  feed_ration_kg = 0,
  feed_byproducts_kg = 0,
  feed_proteins_kg = 0,
  feed_corn_kg = 0,
  feed_soy_kg = 0,
  feed_wheat_kg = 0,
  region = "global",
  fert_type = "mixed",
  plastic_type = "mixed",
  include_uncertainty = FALSE,
  transport_km = NULL,
  ef_conc = NULL,
  ef_fert = NULL,
  ef_plastic = NULL,
  boundaries = NULL
)

Arguments

conc_kg

Numeric. Purchased concentrate feed (kg/year). Default = 0.

fert_n_kg

Numeric. Purchased nitrogen fertilizer (kg N/year). Default = 0.

plastic_kg

Numeric. Agricultural plastics used (kg/year). Default = 0.

feed_grain_dry_kg

Numeric. Grain dry (kg/year, DM). Default = 0.

feed_grain_wet_kg

Numeric. Grain wet (kg/year, DM). Default = 0.

feed_ration_kg

Numeric. Ration + lex (kg/year, DM). Default = 0.

feed_byproducts_kg

Numeric. Byproducts (kg/year, DM). Default = 0.

feed_proteins_kg

Numeric. Proteins (kg/year, DM). Default = 0.

feed_corn_kg

Numeric. Corn grain specific (kg/year, DM). Default = 0.

feed_soy_kg

Numeric. Soybean meal specific (kg/year, DM). Default = 0.

feed_wheat_kg

Numeric. Wheat grain specific (kg/year, DM). Default = 0.

region

Character. Geographic region for emission factors. Options: "EU", "US", "Brazil", "Argentina", "Australia", "global". Default = "global".

fert_type

Character. Fertilizer type. Options: "urea", "ammonium_nitrate", "mixed", "organic". Default = "mixed".

plastic_type

Character. Plastic type. Options: "LDPE", "HDPE", "PP", "mixed". Default = "mixed".

include_uncertainty

Logical. Include uncertainty ranges in output? Default = FALSE.

transport_km

Numeric. Average transport distance for feeds (km). Default = NULL.

ef_conc

Numeric. Override EF for concentrate feed (kg CO2eq/kg). Default = NULL.

ef_fert

Numeric. Override EF for N fertilizer (kg CO2eq/kg N). Default = NULL.

ef_plastic

Numeric. Override EF for plastic (kg CO2eq/kg). Default = NULL.

boundaries

Optional. An object from set_system_boundaries().

Value

A list with emissions (kg CO2eq) by input, uncertainties, and metadata.

Examples

# Basic usage with regional factors
calc_emissions_inputs(
  conc_kg = 1000,
  feed_soy_kg = 500,
  fert_n_kg = 200,
  region = "EU"
)
